dc_title_s: Roads and ROW: Juneau County, Wisconsin, 2019
dct_alternativeTitle_sm: Roads and ROW Juneau County, WI 2019
dc_description_s: This data represents roads and Right Of Ways (ROW) for Juneau County, Wisconsin in 2019 and includes the layers 'Juneau_Roads_2019' and 'Juneau_ROW_2019'. Roads: [Roads data contain the centerlines of all the roads in the county. They are coded by class being: 5 - Interstates, 4 - US Highways, 3 - State Highways, 2 - County Trunk Roads, 1 - Town/Local Roads and 0 - Private Roads, Trails or Alleys. They also have an address range assigned to them with a right and left to and from range, the centerlines broken down into segments with what community (zipcode) they are in, and also what emergency zone (ESN) they fall in.]
